{"tid":216531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怒逼客人簽約，健身中心經理威嚇銷售判160小時社服令","createTime":"2017-04-25T09:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T06:25:07.000Z","uid":81569,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afe9235829ff97d915ea51bc9abf5ad71b8841f9","tid":216531,"uid":81569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"健身中心Fighting Arts Center職員涉以免費體驗為由，擅自以女生信用卡簽帳購入逾萬元課程，女生得知受騙後反抗不果，在後來加入調停的中心經理動怒威迫下妥協，終改簽一份近2000元合約。涉事經理早前承認一項作出具威嚇性營業行為，今早在西九龍裁判法院被判160小時社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n被告林學文（30歲）的代表律師指出，被告的社會服務令報告正面，又說被告背景良好，對事件感到後悔，早前被還押14天已令他受到很大教訓。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，即使被告初次干犯此類涉及不良銷售行為罪行，亦可被判監，惟考慮到被告的社會服務令報告正面，相信已被還押14天的被告已上了寶貴一課，遂判被告接受160小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"b29cd4ef87df1b6d7cd7ec4a8ee64e8df75bbfdc","tid":216531,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08a7b5b636893eb285390ec3aa731fcde94102d","tid":216531,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"其實都幾撚痴線<br />\n明搶你張卡"},{"pid":"ed5f4a9ca12332345c037942118d2cc651fc720f","tid":216531,"uid":25213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"咁都唔洗坐監，唔怪得黑店越開越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c51e22b101009165b447bf9d8ec57c181aed3a","tid":216531,"uid":43510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"偷人成萬蚊都唔洗坐監，痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e667373ca4dd4b940d350e0d3b437c92f2805bc","tid":216531,"uid":81569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>偷人成萬蚊都唔洗坐監，痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq